articles.title: OFFICIAL GRID: Aston Martin and Haas drivers all to start from pit lane - Formula 1
articles.description: The start of the United States Grand Prix will feature something rather unusual for 2023 - very little chance of a Red Bull leading into Turn 1. Instead it's likely to be a Ferrari, McLaren or Mercedes seizing the early advantage in Austin.
